    "This helps them optimize resource allocation and ensure sustainable farming practices, even in the face of changing environmental conditions and limited resources (Roy and Aslekar 2022).",
    "Animal tracking/control Animal tracking and control is greatly facilitated by wearable IoT devices.",
    "These devices track important fitness indicators, such as activity levels, rumination patterns, and vital biometric data.",
    "This tracking helps to detect illnesses early and ultimately reduces mortality rates among livestock (Nigade et al. 2023).",
